<title>USA: Glengate says American Marketing buys shrs.</title>
<headline>Glengate says American Marketing buys shrs.</headline>
<dateline>MOUNTAINSIDE, N.J. 1997-06-27</dateline>
<text>
<p>GlenGate Apparel Inc said Friday American Marketing Industries Inc agreed to buy 23 percent of its total outstanding shares for $2.5 million.</p>
<p>In addition, a separate license agreement has been signed whereby, on April 1, 1998, AMI, through its Swingster division, will become the exclusive domestic marketer of GlenGate products to the corporate catalog marketplace.</p>
